				<category><![CDATA[遊戲專區]]></category>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://34.83.168.187/?p=621</guid>

					<description><![CDATA[市面上有唔同架設Minecraft 伺服器嘅方法，但大部份較為繁複。為左幫大家慳時間，FFRabbit 希望係度同大家分享一個可以係唔同私人網絡嘅情況下架設Minecraft 伺服器嘅方法。 1 下載Minecraft 首先，下載Minecraft。Minecraft 官網：https://www.minecraft.net/en-us/download/（請支持正版） 2 下載Hamachi 然後，你會需要一個虛擬私人網絡，而虛擬私人網絡嘅架設可以交比Hamachi 解決。Hamachi 官網：https://www.vpn.net/ 3 Hamachi 設定（主辦） 接下來，主辦會需要申請一個Hamachi 帳戶。完成後可以按下程式上方嘅Network-&#62; Create a new network。然後設置ID 及密碼。 4 Hamachi 設定（玩家） 玩家亦需要申請一個Hamachi 帳戶。完成後可以按下程式上方嘅Network-&#62; Join an existing network。然後輸入由主辦設置嘅ID 及密碼。 5 Minecraft 設定（主辦） 最後，主辦需要開啟並進入Minecraft World 按ESC-&#62; Open to LAN-&#62; Start LAN World。右下方對話框會出現一個5 位數字，請將呢5 個數字交比玩家們。 6 Minecraft 設定（玩家） 玩家需要按 Multiplayer-&#62; Direct Connection 然後輸入下圖主辦嘅IP＋：＋（上述5&#8230;&#160;<a href="./../../../2020/07/minecraft-java-edition-10%e5%88%86%e9%90%98%e5%85%a7%e6%9e%b6%e8%a8%adminecraft-%e4%bc%ba%e6%9c%8d%e5%99%a8%ef%bc%81%ef%bc%81/index.html" class="" rel="bookmark">Read More &#187;<span class="screen-reader-text">[Minecraft Java Edition] 10分鐘內架設Minecraft 伺服器！！</span></a>]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<p>市面上有唔同架設Minecraft 伺服器嘅方法，但大部份較為繁複。為左幫大家慳時間，FFRabbit 希望係度同大家分享一個可以係唔同私人網絡嘅情況下架設Minecraft 伺服器嘅方法。</p>



<p>1 下載Minecraft</p>



<p>首先，下載Minecraft。Minecraft 官網：<a href="https://www.minecraft.net/en-us/download/" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank">https://www.minecraft.net/en-us/download/</a>（請支持正版）</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img loading="lazy" width="1024" height="738" src="http://34.83.168.187/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Minecraft-server-1-1024x738.png" alt="" class="wp-image-625" srcset="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Minecraft-server-1-1024x738.png 1024w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Minecraft-server-1-300x216.png 300w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Minecraft-server-1-768x554.png 768w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Minecraft-server-1.png 1207w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>2 下載Hamachi</p>



<p>然後，你會需要一個虛擬私人網絡，而虛擬私人網絡嘅架設可以交比Hamachi 解決。Hamachi 官網：<a href="https://www.vpn.net/" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank">https://www.vpn.net/</a></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img loading="lazy" width="1024" height="809" src="http://34.83.168.187/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Minecraft-server-2-1024x809.png" alt="" class="wp-image-626" srcset="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Minecraft-server-2.png 1024w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Minecraft-server-2-300x237.png 300w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Minecraft-server-2-768x606.png 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>3 Hamachi 設定（主辦）</p>



<p>接下來，主辦會需要申請一個Hamachi 帳戶。完成後可以按下程式上方嘅Network-&gt; Create a new network。然後設置ID 及密碼。</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img loading="lazy" width="437" height="371" src="http://34.83.168.187/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Minecraft-server-4.png" alt="" class="wp-image-628" srcset="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Minecraft-server-4.png 437w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Minecraft-server-4-300x255.png 300w" sizes="(max-width: 437px) 100vw, 437px" /></figure></div>



<p>4 Hamachi 設定（玩家）</p>



<p>玩家亦需要申請一個Hamachi 帳戶。完成後可以按下程式上方嘅Network-&gt; Join an existing network。然後輸入由主辦設置嘅ID 及密碼。</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img loading="lazy" width="413" height="189" src="http://34.83.168.187/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Minecraft-server-5.png" alt="" class="wp-image-629" srcset="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Minecraft-server-5.png 413w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Minecraft-server-5-300x137.png 300w" sizes="(max-width: 413px) 100vw, 413px" /></figure></div>



<p>5 Minecraft 設定（主辦）</p>



<p>最後，主辦需要開啟並進入Minecraft World 按ESC-&gt; Open to LAN-&gt; Start LAN World。右下方對話框會出現一個5 位數字，請將呢5 個數字交比玩家們。</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img loading="lazy" width="854" height="475" src="http://34.83.168.187/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Minecraft-server-6.png" alt="" class="wp-image-630" srcset="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Minecraft-server-6.png 854w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Minecraft-server-6-300x167.png 300w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Minecraft-server-6-768x427.png 768w" sizes="(max-width: 854px) 100vw, 854px" /></figure></div>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img loading="lazy" width="850" height="474" src="http://34.83.168.187/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Minecraft-server-8.png" alt="" class="wp-image-631" srcset="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Minecraft-server-8.png 850w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Minecraft-server-8-300x167.png 300w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Minecraft-server-8-768x428.png 768w" sizes="(max-width: 850px) 100vw, 850px" /></figure></div>



<p>6 Minecraft 設定（玩家）</p>



<p>玩家需要按 Multiplayer-&gt; Direct Connection 然後輸入下圖主辦嘅IP＋：＋（上述5 位數字）。例如：123.12.123.123:12345</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img loading="lazy" width="261" height="124" src="http://34.83.168.187/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Minecraft-server-3.png" alt="" class="wp-image-627"/></figure></div>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img loading="lazy" width="852" height="477" src="http://34.83.168.187/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Minecraft-server-10.png" alt="" class="wp-image-632" srcset="./../../../wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Minecraft-server-10.png 852w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Minecraft-server-10-300x168.png 300w, ./../../../wp-content/uploads/2020/07/Minecraft-server-10-768x430.png 768w" sizes="(max-width: 852px) 100vw, 852px" /></figure></div>



<p>7 注意事項</p>



<p>使用呢個方法有幾個需要注意嘅事項。首先，主辦嘅電腦會負責大部分運算工作，所以需要一部性能比較好嘅電腦。其次，Server 只會係主辦上線（Open LAN）嘅時候存在，所以玩家們只可以係主辦上線嘅時候進入Server。最後，此方法只適用係Minecraft Java Edition，而人數上限為5 人。</p>
]]></content:encoded>
					
		
		
